    "digital painting.html": {
      "settings": {
        "meta_descr": "I will recreate your memories into a piece of art which will be a perfect present for your most beloved. \nBut first, I'd love to talk to you about what style of Artwork you are looking for, for example more realistic or more artistic.\nWhy wait? Upload a photo and I’ll turn it in to an amazing piece of art. ",
        "title": "Besim Mikullovci | Digital Painting",
        "order": 5,
        "header_custom": ""
      },
