    "book_illustration.html": {
      "settings": {
        "meta_descr": "I offer book illustration services for global clients, whether it's children's book illustrations or drawings to accompany poetry.\n\n\nAn illustration is something unavoidable in poetry and other kind of books, so, whether you are a self-publishing author or a publishing company looking for stunning book illustrations at a reasonable price you are in the right place.\nProfessional book illustrators working with me are skilled in designing all types of illustrations from minimalist, classic, modern or expressive ones. \n",
        "title": "Besim Mikullovci | Book Illustration",
        "order": 3
      },
