    "brandidentity.html": {
      "settings": {
        "meta_descr": "Brand identity is the best way any business, agency, or nonprofit can gain a competitive advantage. It starts by designing a logo which is just one part of a brand.\nA strong brand identity doesn’t happen overnight. You can’t just pick a few colors and slap together a logo. You need to approach your design strategically.\n\n This requires deep thinking, a team with strong communication and design skills, and an intimate understanding of your brand.\n\nYour brand is the single most important investment you can make in your business\n",
        "title": "Besim Mikullovci | Brand Identity",
        "order": 17,
        "header_custom": ""
      },
